<Author>sunnygirldi
<Content>comfortable and clean We stayed at this hotel the evening before our cruise. They provided transportation from the airport. They advertised 24 hour shuttle but because of being brand new, they didn't have the need for a 24 hour shuttle so when we called the hotel upon our airport arrival, they had us take a cab. We pulled up to the hotel and they paid the driver. Check in was fast efficient and friendly. Rooms were perfectly clean and beds were comfortable. Originally I was concerned about airport noise but there wasn't any. Rooms were quiet. For the breakfast the next morning, we walked right across the street to Dennys. I would definately stay at this hotel again. 
