<Author>Bryan_m36
<Content>Great first time stay! A brand new hotel. So what can you expect. Only the best. From check-in to check-out, everything went smoothly. Staff was exceptionally friendly. As a Diamond member from Hilton, I was very sattisfied with this stay. This was my first but certainly not the last visit to the HGI. Room was nicely decorated with flat screen tv. The bed was great. Breakfast was very good. No complaints at all. Highly recommended and good location. Several junkfood chains near the hotel, So food wise you are not going to have problems. 
